description: The Green Meanie is a Columbus food truck with a fun, unique, and eclectic menu. The menu explores and combines unique flavors and textures, drawing from a variety of cultural influences. Green Meanie is about having fun with food and utilizing the finest and freshest ingredients and supporting local vendors. The concept was developed by Keith and Janka Smith and partner Shawn Head. Keith is the mastermind behind the menu, giving all of the credit for his culinary skills to his mother and her flawless country cooking. The Green Meanie crew has a passion for food and fun and hopes to bring another unique aspect to Columbus' exciting food scene!
name: The Green Meanie
